.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/109%2c%e5%8e%9f%e8%a8%b4%2c41%2c20210318%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,109,原訴,41,20210318,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"原訴","JNO":"41","JDATE":"20210318","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}